          <li>Document storage and management</li>
          <li>Communication tools for boards and residents</li>
          <li>Compliance tracking and deadline reminders</li>
          <li>Maintenance request management</li>
          <li>Mobile applications for iOS and Android</li>
          <li>Public-facing community websites</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. User Accounts</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          When you create an account with us, you must provide accurate, complete, and current information. Failure to do so constitutes a breach of the Terms.
