          You retain ownership of any content you upload to the Service. By uploading content, you grant us a license to use, store, and process that content to provide the Service to you and your association.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">Association Data</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Data uploaded to the Service on behalf of a condominium association remains the property of that association. Access to association data is governed by the association's bylaws and applicable Florida law.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">Data Export</h3>
